Class WordAdapter

com.example.sesion5.model.WordAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class WordAdapter extends Object implements IWord
An abstract class that provides a partial implementation of the IWord interface. It serves as a base for concrete implementations of word validation and processing.
